--------------------------------------
None


ctphase - Event phase computation
---------------------------------
None


cscripts
--------
Use t-type parameters for "tmin" and "tmax" to all specifying times in various
formats (#1864).

The script csphagen was added to allow the generation of PHA, ARF and RMF datasets
for classical On/Off IACT analysis (#2208).


